'''尼羅河歧鬚鮠'''（[[學名|學名]]：'''''Synodontis batensoda'''''）是[[倒立鯰科|倒立鯰科]]下的一種[[鯰魚|鯰魚]]。生活在[[尼羅河|尼羅河]]、[[乍得盆地|乍得盆地]]、[[尼日爾河|尼日爾河]]、[[塞內加爾河|塞內加爾河]]以及[[岡比亞河|岡比亞河]]流域。

尼羅河歧鬚鮠有39–42個[[鳃耙|鳃耙]]，而同屬的其他鯰魚一般只有7個–33個，其[[背鰭|背鰭]]和[[脂鰭|脂鰭]]相連，身體短粗，灰黑色有褐色斑點。其[[鰓蓋|鰓蓋]]附近有小棘刺。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Friel, John P. & Thomas R. Vigliotta |year=2006 |title=''Synodontis acanthoperca'', a new species from the Ogôoué River system, Gabon with comments on spiny ornamentation and sexual dimorphism in mochokid catfishes (Siluriformes: Mochokidae) |journal=[[Zootaxa|Zootaxa]] |volume=1125 |pages=45–56 |url=http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2006f/zt01125p056.pdf |format=[[Portable_Document_Format|PDF]] |access-date=2013-09-06 |archive-date=2013-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523205437/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2006f/zt01125p056.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>其[[魚鬚|魚鬚]]上有一層薄膜。<ref name=pc>PlanetCatfish (2006): [http://www.planetcatfish.com/catelog/species.php?species_id=780 ''Brachysynodontis batensoda''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.planetcatfish.com/catelog/species.php?species_id=780 |date=20090110095105 }}. Version of June 17, 2006. Retrieved August 2, 2007.</ref>與屬內的其他生物一般，尼羅河歧鬚鮠幾乎是顛倒著頭朝下遊動覓食。<ref name=pc/>其體長可達{{convert|50|cm|in}}，重達{{convert|1.5|kg|lb}}。<ref name=fishbase>{{FishBase species|genus=Synodontis |species=batensoda|year=2011|month=December}}</ref>

尼羅河歧鬚鮠有是一種[[雜食動物|雜食動物]]，以[[浮游生物|浮游生物]]、[[水藻|水藻]]、[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]、[[軟體動物|軟體動物]]等為食。<ref name=fishbase/>性情溫和。<ref name=pc/>

